{"data":[{"name":"97:1","price":"ನಿಶ್ಚಯವಾಗಿಯೂ ನಾವು ಇದನ್ನು (ಕುರ್‌ಆನನ್ನು) ನಿರ್ಣಯದ ರಾತ್ರಿಯಲ್ಲಿ ಅವತೀರ್ಣಗೊಳಿಸಿದ್ದೇವೆ.[1]","arabic":"إِنَّآ أَنزَلۡنَٰهُ فِي لَيۡلَةِ ٱلۡقَدۡرِ","category":["97 (Al-Qadr)","Al-Qadr","Surah Al-Qadr"],"ayahNumber":6126,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1] ನಿರ್ಣಯದ ರಾತ್ರಿ (ಲೈಲತುಲ್ ಕದ್ರ್) ಯಲ್ಲಿ ಪವಿತ್ರ ಕುರ್‌ಆನ್ ಅನ್ನು ಲೌಹುಲ್ ಮಹ್ಫೂಝ್ (ಸುರಕ್ಷಿತ ಫಲಕ) ನಿಂದ ಆಕಾಶದಲ್ಲಿರುವ ಬೈತುಲ್ ಇಝ್ಝತ್‌ಗೆ ಇಳಿಸಲಾಯಿತು. ಅಲ್ಲಿಂದ ಅದು 23 ವರ್ಷಗಳ ಕಾಲ ಹಂತ ಹಂತವಾಗಿ ಮತ್ತು ಸಾಂದರ್ಭಿಕವಾಗಿ ಭೂಲೋಕಕ್ಕೆ ಅವತೀರ್ಣವಾಯಿತು. ನಿರ್ಣಯದ ರಾತ್ರಿ (ಲೈಲತುಲ್ ಕದ್ರ್) ರಮದಾನ್ ತಿಂಗಳ ಕೊನೆಯ ಹತ್ತರ ಬೆಸ ರಾತ್ರಿಗಳಲ್ಲಿ ಬರುತ್ತದೆ.","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"innā anzalnāhu fī laylati al-qadri ","translations":["Indeed, We","revealed it","in","(the) Night","(of) Power","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["innā","anzalnāhu","fī","laylati","al-qadri",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2949],[2,2949,5469],[3,5469,5939],[4,5939,6759],[5,6759,7884]]}},{"name":"97:2","price":"ನಿರ್ಣಯದ ರಾತ್ರಿ ಏನೆಂದು ನಿಮಗೇನು ಗೊತ್ತು?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا لَيۡلَةُ ٱلۡقَدۡرِ","category":["97 (Al-Qadr)","Al-Qadr","Surah Al-Qadr"],"ayahNumber":6127,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā adrāka mā laylatu al-qadri ","translations":["And what","can make you know","what","(the) Night","(of) Power (is)","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","adrāka","mā","laylatu","al-qadri",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2130],[2,2130,3260],[3,3260,3670],[4,3670,4480],[5,4480,5945]]}},{"name":"97:3","price":"ನಿರ್ಣಯದ ರಾತ್ರಿಯು ಸಾವಿರ ತಿಂಗಳುಗಳಿಗಿಂತ ಶ್ರೇಷ್ಠವಾಗಿದೆ.","arabic":"لَيۡلَةُ ٱلۡقَدۡرِ خَيۡرٞ مِّنۡ أَلۡفِ شَهۡرٖ","category":["97 (Al-Qadr)","Al-Qadr","Surah Al-Qadr"],"ayahNumber":6128,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"laylatu al-qadri khayrun min alfi shahrin ","translations":["(The) Night","(of) Power","(is) better","than","a thousand","month(s)","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["laylatu","al-qadri","khayrun","min","alfi","shahrin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,890],[2,890,1700],[3,1700,2380],[4,2380,3740],[5,3740,4300],[6,4300,5465]]}},{"name":"97:4","price":"ಆ ರಾತ್ರಿಯಲ್ಲಿ ಎಲ್ಲಾ ಕಾರ್ಯಗಳನ್ನು ಜಾರಿಗೊಳಿಸುವುದಕ್ಕಾಗಿ ದೇವದೂತರು‍ಗಳು ಮತ್ತು ರೂಹ್ (ಜಿಬ್ರೀಲ್) ತಮ್ಮ ಪರಿಪಾಲಕನ (ಅಲ್ಲಾಹನ) ಅಪ್ಪಣೆಯೊಂದಿಗೆ ಇಳಿದು ಬರುವರು.","arabic":"تَنَزَّلُ ٱلۡمَلَٰٓئِكَةُ وَٱلرُّوحُ فِيهَا بِإِذۡنِ رَبِّهِم مِّن كُلِّ أَمۡرٖ","category":["97 (Al-Qadr)","Al-Qadr","Surah Al-Qadr"],"ayahNumber":6129,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"tanazzalu al-malāikatu wal-rūḥu fīhā bi-idh'ni rabbihim min kulli amrin ","translations":["Descend","the Angels","and the Spirit","therein","by (the) permission","(of) their Lord","for","every","affair","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["tanazzalu","al-malāikatu","wal-rūḥu","fīhā","bi-idh'ni","rabbihim","min","kulli","amrin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1030],[2,1030,4070],[3,4070,5000],[4,5000,5900],[5,5900,6600],[6,6600,7610],[7,7610,9520],[8,9520,10110],[9,10110,10715]]}},{"name":"97:5","price":"ಆ ರಾತ್ರಿಯು ಪ್ರಭಾತೋದಯದ ತನಕ ಸಂಪೂರ್ಣ ಶಾಂತಿಯುತವಾಗಿರುವುದು.","arabic":"سَلَٰمٌ هِيَ حَتَّىٰ مَطۡلَعِ ٱلۡفَجۡرِ","category":["97 (Al-Qadr)","Al-Qadr","Surah Al-Qadr"],"ayahNumber":6130,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn","meta":{"transliteration":"salāmun hiya ḥattā maṭlaʿi al-fajri ","translations":["Peace","it (is)","until","(the) emergence","(of) the dawn","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["salāmun","hiya","ḥattā","maṭlaʿi","al-fajri",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,1580],[3,1580,2480],[4,2480,3390],[5,3390,5085]]}}],"chapter":["97 (Al-Qadr)","Al-Qadr","Surah Al-Qadr","Chapter Al-Qadr","Qadr","Surah Qadr","Chapter Qadr","Al Qadr","Surah Al Qadr","Chapter Al Qadr","Surah 97","Chapter 97","The Power","القدر"],"version":{"key":"kannada_hamza","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"kn","version":"1.0.3","last_update":1710623781,"title":"Kannada translation","description":"Translation of the meanings of the Noble Qur’an into the Kannada language, translated by Muhammad Hamza Battur."}}